Project Omni is a dedicated project created to build multiple Operating Systems and other software for micro-devices. 
Project Omni was established on 3/1/2026 and currently has adequate funding for the year of 2026.
Funding for the year 2027 is still unclear but the project will still dedicate itself to make Operating Systems and other software for micro-devices.

Project Omni is currently working on House 26 for the Orignal Thumby. 
We are still deciding which micro-device will get the honor of House 27 for the year 2027 but it is likely that the M5Stack Cardputer will get the honor next year.
In the case that funding of Project Omni is not secured for 2027, the owner of Project Omni will support it with his own funds and try to uplift the project until funding is secured.

-From the Staff of Project Omni
